contentList.content: Sights of the Seelie: Summon Archfey

The archfey can cast <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_PixieWhispers">Dissonant Whispers</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_PixieDut">Pixie Dust</LSTag>, and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_PixieStep">Misty Step</LSTag>.

Conjure an archfey to fight alongside you. It can cast <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_PixieWhispers">Dissonant Whispers</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_PixieDut">Pixie Dust</LSTag>, and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_PixieStep">Misty Step</LSTag>.
